    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得你的电脑桌面有些枯燥？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面猫猫来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的小猫咪将会陪伴你工作、学习、发呆……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫猫会提醒你按时休息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫猫还可能会带给你特殊的礼物哦~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=93 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面猫猫是一款可爱的挂机猫猫桌宠，在挂机的过程中，猫猫会为你带回各种各样的礼物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集这些礼物，了解猫猫的冒险生活，还可以解锁成就哦~</p>",
